{"tid":33584,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"46歲顏仟汶分居搞離婚 Fit爆身型願再拍三級片","createTime":"2016-12-11T01:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T23:53:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5e3fe403e39f6e588372e0b0a5227ab2f1e83d","tid":33584,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T01:47:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161205/photo/bkn-20161205230435943-1205_00862_001_02b.jpg?20161206004000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20161205%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161205230435943-1205_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20161206004000&h=4241ea7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現年46歲的顏仟汶（Sophie）一直與圈外老公相親相愛，結婚八年的她卻向東網自揭正與對方搞離婚，更已服用情緒藥兩年，而Sophie現在更於錦田獨居，出出入入形單影隻。而講到與老公分居，Sophie更即場爆喊！<br />\n<br />\n談到她曾於1998年與杜汶澤相戀，卻因為田蕊妮介入而分手，問到現時會否嬲女方做第三者？她表示早已放下：「&amp;#22000;陣時都冇嬲過田蕊妮，更何況依家，亦唔覺得杜汶澤對我唔住，因為知佢已經唔愛你，十幾年前&amp;#22021;事，咩都淡化晒啦！」<br />\n<br />\n演藝路一波三折<br />\n<br />\n入行27年的Sophie試過拍無&amp;#32171;劇捱到肝炎，亦試過為生活做接待員，更試過因為幫雜誌影性感相，簽約後短短10個月被亞視炒魷魚，演藝路上可謂一波三折。無奈要向生活低頭的她，當年不幸得悉父親患上食道癌，需要籌措醫藥費，適逢王晶和李兆基找她接拍三級片，她只好答應：「個數字好吸引，我細佬妹仲細，但唔可以賴屋企人，係我自己冇計劃過。（有冇後悔？）其實我希望時間可以倒流，去番我中一時，畀心機讀好&amp;#21874;書，唔入娛樂圈。」<br />\n<br />\n身材依然Fit爆<br />\n<br />\n曾為家庭而「獻身」的Sophie在訪問中邊哭邊說幸好父親身體比起以前好好多，細妹已出身之餘，細佬亦大學畢業，總算鬆一口氣。拍過一套三點盡露、四套露兩點三級片的她表示前後參與過半百套三級片的演出，更謂就算再拍三級片也不介意。雖然現時已經46歲，但其32C導彈卻零漏氣&amp;#36857;象，即使穿起水&amp;#30528;亦絕不比其他少女輸蝕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161205/photo/bkn-20161205230556164-1205_00862_001_03b.jpg?20161205233053\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20161205%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161205230556164-1205_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20161205233053&h=cff7955f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161205/photo/bkn-20161205230556164-1205_00862_001_04b.jpg?20161205233053\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20161205%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161205230556164-1205_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20161205233053&h=feefa228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161205/photo/bkn-20161205230435943-1205_00862_001_09b.jpg?20161206004000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20161205%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161205230435943-1205_00862_001_09b.jpg%3F20161206004000&h=c8527fec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161205/photo/bkn-20161205230556164-1205_00862_001_02b.jpg?20161205233053\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20161205%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161205230556164-1205_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20161205233053&h=4ed2f078&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161205/photo/bkn-20161205230556164-1205_00862_001_06b.jpg?20161205233053\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20161205%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161205230556164-1205_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20161205233053&h=27d46e27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a672dc5a457ccd960676d00d559cca9feb8df19a","tid":33584,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T01:48:23.000Z","msg":"milf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29ed19626f0bbe3f024089fab596f3e07db5b53","tid":33584,"uid":39780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T01:48:31.000Z","msg":"比盡100"},{"pid":"ae133e9c654422c6a37015f82ae8e930f2e301a7","tid":33584,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T01:49:03.000Z","msg":"D皮好鬆下啦喎😂"},{"pid":"2def4a0d197d04277128b9c19a641e080acebe95","tid":33584,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"難聽啲講你拍都未必有人睇<img src=\"/